# 🛒 E-Commerce REST API

🚀 A secure and scalable **RESTful backend** for an e-commerce platform built with **Java & Spring Boot**.
This project provides APIs for **authentication, product management, shopping cart operations, and order processing** following a clean layered architecture.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🧰 Tech Stack

☕ **Java**
🌱 **Spring Boot**
🔐 **Spring Security + JWT**
🗄 **MySQL Database**
📦 **Maven**
🧪 **Postman**
🐙 **Git & GitHub**

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ✨ Features

👤 **User Module**

* 📝 User Registration
* 🔑 Secure Login with JWT
* 👥 Role-Based Access (Admin / Customer)

📦 **Product Module**

* ➕ Add Products (Admin)
* ✏ Update Products
* ❌ Delete Products
* 🔍 Search by Category / Name
* 📋 View Product Catalog

🛒 **Cart Module**

* ➕ Add Items to Cart
* 🔄 Update Quantity
* ❌ Remove Items
* 👀 View Cart Details

📑 **Order Module**

* 🧾 Place Orders
* 📚 View Order History
* 🚚 Track Order Status

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 📁 Project Structure

src
┣ 📂 controller → REST API endpoints
┣ 📂 service → business logic
┣ 📂 repository → database layer
┣ 📂 model → entity classes
┣ 📂 dto → data transfer objects
┗ 📂 config → security & JWT configuration

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## 🔗 Sample API Endpoints

🔐 Authentication
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/login

📦 Products
GET    /api/products
POST   /api/products
PUT    /api/products/{id}
DELETE /api/products/{id}

🛒 Cart
POST   /api/cart/add
GET    /api/cart
DELETE /api/cart/{productId}

📑 Orders
POST   /api/orders
GET    /api/orders/user

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ▶ Run the Project

1️⃣ **Clone the repository**

git clone https://github.com/your-username/ecommerce-rest-api.git

2️⃣ **Configure MySQL in `application.properties`**

spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ecommerce
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=yourpassword

3️⃣ **Run the application**

mvn spring-boot:run

🌐 Server will start at
http://localhost:8080

